263
00:21:32,712 --> 00:21:34,987
Well, wouldn't want to keep Vic waiting.

264
00:21:35,673 --> 00:21:37,903
Reed, what are you doing here?

265
00:21:38,176 --> 00:21:39,370
I thought...

