for me and some other guy?

308
00:24:09,911 --> 00:24:11,663
Victor may be a lot of things.

309
00:24:11,829 --> 00:24:14,821
But at least he's not afraid
to fight for what he wants.

310
00:24:15,166 --> 00:24:17,441
