314
00:24:30,556 --> 00:24:32,387
What do you mean, you can't?
Look at me!

315
00:24:32,558 --> 00:24:34,276
Sue, look at your hands!

316
00:24:53,788 --> 00:24:55,426
Hey, you guys.

317
00:24:56,624 --> 00:24:59,092
You are never gonna believe
what just happened to me.

318
00:24:59,293 --> 00:25:00,408
What?

319
00:25:01,796 --> 00:25:03,832
Well, I can explain this.

320
00:25:31,367 --> 00:25:34,598
It has to be the cloud.
It's fundamentally altered our DNA.

321
00:25:34,829 --> 00:25:36,342
Let's not jump to conclusions.

322
00:25:36,497 --> 00:25:39,295
We need a massive amount of evidence
before making that leap.

323
00:25:39,500 --> 00:25:41,013
Guys, look!

324
00:25:51,596 --> 00:25:54,633
Now, picture that, but everywhere.

325
00:25:55,933 --> 00:25:58,003
It was everywhere.

326
00:25:59,062 --> 00:26:00,097
What?

327
00:26:02,065 --> 00:26:04,499
The cloud has fundamentally altered
our DNA.

328
00:26:05,777 --> 00:26:07,733
- Cool!
- We need to find Ben.

329
