And you know what, guys?
I think I was flying.

330
00:26:16,996 --> 00:26:18,429
I said, cut it out, Johnny.

331
00:26:18,581 --> 00:26:19,980
I'm getting the hang of it.

332
00:26:20,124 --> 00:26:22,194
- Ben, it's Reed.
- Stop.

333
00:26:22,377 --> 00:26:23,776
- All right.
- All right?

334
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,194
