to exposure from the cloud.

354
00:28:00,433 --> 00:28:02,742
We all have different symptoms.

355
00:28:02,935 --> 00:28:04,050
Symptoms?

356
00:28:04,187 --> 00:28:07,020
- Victor, I should have...
- Just find him.

357
00:28:09,984 --> 00:28:12,578
Anybody got any ideas
where the big guy's going?

358
00:28:16,532 --> 00:28:17,965
