360
00:29:06,082 --> 00:29:07,356
Little buttons.

361
00:29:08,001 --> 00:29:09,434
Hello, Operator?

362
00:29:12,922 --> 00:29:14,594
<i>- Hello?</i>
- Debs?

363
00:29:15,299 --> 00:29:16,857
- It's me.
<i>- Ben?</i>

364
00:29:17,802 --> 00:29:20,316
<i>Are you all right?</i>
<i>You sound a little different. </i>

365
00:29:20,596 --> 00:29:23,315
- Listen, I need you to come out front.
<i>- Out front?</i>

366
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:25,579
<i>You're home, baby?</i>

367
00:29:26,477 --> 00:29:27,466
<i>Yeah. </i>

368
00:29:29,939 --> 00:29:31,850
