Yeah, I got a little one for you, too.

370
00:29:40,575 --> 00:29:41,690
Ben?

371
00:29:45,121 --> 00:29:46,554
Where are you?

372
00:29:46,956 --> 00:29:48,389
I'm over here.

373
00:29:49,125 --> 00:29:51,514
Don't come any closer for a sec, okay?

374
00:29:52,670 --> 00:29:55,707
It's gonna be a bit of a shock.

375
00:29:55,923 --> 00:29:57,720
Honey, what's going on?

376
00:29:58,134 --> 00:29:59,283
Debs...

377
00:30:00,470 --> 00:30:02,700
remember when we used to say...

378
00:30:03,139 --> 00:30:05,937
together forever no matter what?

379
00:30:06,851 --> 00:30:07,966
Yeah.

380
00:30:09,395 --> 00:30:10,669
Well...

381
00:30:11,147 --> 00:30:12,899
Baby, you're scaring me.

382
00:30:26,996 --> 00:30:28,111
Oh, my God.

383
00:30:28,831 --> 00:30:31,550
Deb, it's me. It's still me.

384
00:30:31,751 --> 00:30:33,469
It was the accident. Let me explain.

385
00:30:33,628 --> 00:30:35,698
- No! Don't touch me!
- Debs!

386
00:30:42,804 --> 00:30:44,396
